Package: shadowfetch-creative-base
Source: shadowfetch-meta
Version: 1.0.0-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Shadowfetch Project <maintainers@shadowfetch.example>
Installed-Size: 7
Depends: gimp, krita, inkscape, darktable, rawtherapee, ardour, audacity, lsp-plugins, x42-plugins, calf-plugins, kdenlive, obs-studio, ffmpeg, fonts-inter
Recommends: blender, lmms, carla, fonts-jetbrains-mono
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://shadowfetch.example/
Description: Shadowfetch creative app baseline
 Installs the core set of creative applications Shadowfetch users
 expect: 2D, 3D, photo, audio, and video tools. Packages not currently
 available in Debian testing under their expected names (blender, lmms,
 carla, fonts-jetbrains-mono) are listed as Recommends so install
 doesn't fail — Flatpak fallbacks are offered in the welcome wizard.
